43 SECTION 5.9.(b) The funds set out in subsection (a) of this section may be
44 reallocated only when all of the following conditions are met:
45 (1) The appropriated funds have not been expended by December 31, 2025.
46 (2) There is a reasonable expectation that the funds will not be expended before
47 the deadline established by applicable federal law or guidance.
48 (3) The reallocation is made to support one or more SFRF related activities
49 authorized and receiving appropriations under this act or one of the acts listed
50 above in subsection (a) of this section. Reallocated funds shall not be used for
51 any new activity, purpose, or program.
