43 structured, paid, or other experiential learning in the classroom, including
44 applicable program design and sequencing components needed to achieve that
45 goal.
46 (2) Maximize usage and transferability of at least the following coursework
47 completion opportunities:
48 a. College transfer pathways provided through the Career and College
49 Promise Program that support entry into a recognized educator
50 preparation program.
