1 (1)a. For kindergarten, one teacher per 18 students.
2 (2)b. For first grade, one teacher per 16 students.
3 (3)c. For second grade, one teacher per 17 students.
4 (4)d. For third grade, one teacher per 17 students.
5 In grades four through 12, local school administrative units shall have the maximum
