43 G.S. 116-204(11a).
44 (6) From the total amount of funding appropriated to the Board of Governors of
45 The University of North Carolina and allocated to the Authority in the
46 2025-2026 fiscal year to support the award of scholarship funds under the
47 Program in that fiscal year, the Authority may use up to two and one-half
