43 SECTION 8A.10.(a) Definitions. – The following definitions apply in this section:
44 (1) Academic term. – A semester or summer session.
45 (2) Authority. – The State Education Assistance Authority.
46 (3) Dean. – The Dean of the School of Health Sciences at WSSU.
47 (4) Eligible nurse. – A nurse who meets all of the following criteria:
48 a. Enrolled at WSSU beginning in the 2026-2027 or 2027-2028
49 academic year.
50 b. Received a forgivable loan under the Program.
