1 SECTION 9D.1.(f) Reporting. – The Division of Child Development and Early
2 Education shall submit an annual report no later than March 15 of each year to the Joint
3 Legislative Oversight Committee on Health and Human Services, the Office of State Budget and
4 Management, and the Fiscal Research Division. The report shall include the following:
5 (1) The number of children participating in the NC Pre-K program by county.
