12 (4) The results of an annual evaluation of the NC Pre-K program.
13 SECTION 9D.1.(g) Audits. – The administration of the NC Pre-K program by local
14 partnerships shall be subject to the financial and compliance audits authorized under
15 G.S. 143B-168.14(b).
