27 shall not reduce the allocation for counties with less than 35,000 in population below the
28 2012-2013 funding level.
29 SECTION 9D.5.(g) Performance-Based Evaluation. – The Department of Health
30 and Human Services shall continue to implement the performance-based evaluation system.
