24 percentage for each quarter shall equal the health advancement freestanding psychiatric hospital
25 HASP component calculated under G.S. 108A-147.6A divided by the total hospital costs for all
26 freestanding psychiatric hospitals holding a license on the first day of the assessment quarter."
