44 beginning of each fiscal year relative to single-stream funding, the Department of Health and
45 Human Services, Division of Mental Health, Developmental Disabilities, and Substance Use
46 Services (DMH/DD/SUS), shall distribute not less than one-twelfth of each LME/MCO's base
47 budget allocation at the beginning of the fiscal year and subtract the amount of that distribution
48 from the LME/MCO's total reimbursements for the fiscal year. For each month of the fiscal year
49 after July, DMH/DD/SUS shall distribute, on the third working day of the month, one-eleventh
50 of the amount of each LME/MCO's single-stream allocation that remains after subtracting the
51 amount of the distribution that was made to the LME/MCO in July of the fiscal year.
