25 "§ 130A-33.66. Advisory Council on Rare Diseases; powers and duties; reports.
26 The advisory council shall have the following powers and duties:
27 (1) Advise on coordinating the Governor, the Secretary, and the General
28 Assembly on all of the following:
29 a. Coordination of statewide efforts for the to study of the incidence of
30 rare diseases within the State and the status of the rare disease
31 community.
