15 SECTION 9J.8.(a) Funds appropriated in this act to the Department of Health and
16 Human Services, Division of Social Services (Division), for each year of the 2025-2027 fiscal
17 biennium for a report on certain Supplemental Nutrition Assistance Program (SNAP) and
18 Temporary Assistance for Needy Families (TANF) expenditures shall be allocated for vendor
