46 Development Category in subsection (a) of this section shall be made available as grants for
47 eligible activities listed in this subsection. The funds available for grants under this category may
48 be used for all of the following, subject to the national objectives and eligible activities allowed
49 under guidance issued by HUD:
50 (1) Acquisition of real property.
51 (2) Demolition and rehabilitation of buildings and improvements.
