17 following funds:
18 (1) Contributions made by each State department, agency, and institution that is
19 required under this Article to contribute to the Self-insurance Fund.
20 (2) Transfers from the Enterprise Fund to the Self-insurance Fund for the purpose
21 of paying claims for damage or loss to State property resulting from any peril
22 that are submitted by a State department, agency, or institution in accordance
23 with this Part.
24 (3) Any funds appropriated to the Self-insurance Fund.
