27 (1) Administration of the Self-insurance Fund and the Enterprise Fund. – No more
28 than ten percent (10%) of the amount collected in contributions under this Part
29 in any State fiscal year may be used for the purposes of administering the
30 Self-insurance Fund and the Enterprise Fund and carrying out duties under
31 this Article.
