37 Veterans Affairs for the 2025-2027 fiscal biennium for capital improvements, the Department
38 shall have installed in a prominent location on the grounds of each of the State's four veterans'
39 cemeteries a plaque on which is inscribed President Abraham Lincoln's promise to veterans and
