7 SECTION 43.18.(a) Intent. – It is the intent of the General Assembly to improve the
8 accessibility of and customer service provided by the Division of Motor Vehicles of the
9 Department of Transportation (DMV) by implementing a pilot program in Forsyth County
10 authorizing either the DMV or certain third-party vendors to provide in-home drivers license
