34 the DMV shall award one or more contracts to third-party vendors in Forsyth County. The
35 duration of a contract may not extend beyond January 1, 2029.
36 SECTION 43.18.(d) Pilot Program Implementation Date and Requirements. – The
37 pilot program shall begin January 1, 2027, and, notwithstanding any other provision of law, the
38 selected third-party vendors are authorized to provide in-home drivers license renewal services
