36 schedulers, except devices that are cellular phones; personal digital assistants,
37 except devices that are cellular phones; computer printers; printer supplies for
38 computers; printer paper; and printer ink.
39 (240a) School instructional material. – Written material commonly used by a student
40 in a course of study as a reference and to learn the subject being taught. The
