42 textbooks; and workbooks.
43 (240b) School supply. – An item commonly used by a student in a course of study.
44 The following is an all-inclusive list: binders; book bags; calculators;
45 cellophane tape; blackboard chalk; compasses; composition books; crayons;
46 erasers; folders that are expandable, pocket, plastic, and manila; glue, paste,
47 and paste sticks; highlighters; index card and index card boxes; legal pads;
48 lunch boxes; markers; notebooks; paper that is loose leaf ruled notebook
49 paper, copy paper, graph paper, tracing paper, manila paper, colored paper,
50 poster board, or construction paper; pencil boxes and other school supply
