4 provisions of any legislation enacted during the 2025 Regular Session of the General Assembly
5 affecting the State budget shall remain in effect.
6
7 EFFECT OF HEADINGS
8 SECTION 45.6. The headings to the Parts, subparts, and sections of this act are a
9 convenience to the reader and are for reference only. The headings do not expand, limit, or define
10 the text of this act, except for effective dates referring to a Part or subpart.
